725338f-a.title: Queens: 42nd Avenue - 211th Street
725338f-a.text:
42nd Avenue, south side, at 211th Street, looking eastward
and showing old homes. These stand in the path of the proposed
211th Street, and were the property of R.M. Bell in 1873. 42nd
Avenue, here, was formerly called Palace Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
